name: remember
description:
Remember, remember, the 5th of November

Just for the record, my ancestors were on the side of the anarchists..

This was created by experimenting with the russian version of DALLE, as well as with CLIP guided diffusion and using p5js to process the image prompt, specifically for the mask..

I modeled it off of the Venetian carnival masks, since they aren't owned by a gigantic international entertainment corporation.
